summary: Adding more farm animals to the land of Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
I will be going through and adding more farm animals to each farm in Skyrim with existing animals already in place, to add a little more life to the farm. 

First up is Hod and Gerdur\'s house in Riverwood: added more chickens and nests along with another cow.

**This mod is discontinued, please use Michele Angelo\'s, link below

http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/8565
author: LiquidBronze
